verbose_text: Following osteogenic induction of Vector-cPDLSCs and EfnB2-cPDLSCs, the protein expression levels of collagen I, Runt related transcription factor 2, osteocalcin, ephrin type-B receptor 4 (EphB4), phospho-EphB4, ephrinB2 and phosphoephrinB2 were analyzed by western blot assays.
